* [Setting up NFS howto](https://help.ubuntu.com/community/SettingUpNFSHowTo)

## Steps

* ```apt-get install nfs-kernel-server```
* edit ```/etc/exports```
* ```service nfs-kernel-server restart```

## Mounting on busybox

* ```mount -t nfs -o proto=tcp,port=2049,nolock  <ip>:<path> /<dir>```


